          "description": "I would like to recognize Jonathan Ortiz from Patient Finance at Harlem Hospital for providing exceptional customer service and assistance with my health insurance application. From the very beginning, Jonathan demonstrated professionalism, patience, and a genuine commitment to helping me navigate a process that can often be confusing and stressful.\n\nWhat truly sets Jonathan apart is his dedication to going above and beyond for patients. He took the time to explain every step, answered all of my questions thoroughly, and ensured that I understood my options. His responsiveness, attention to detail, and willingness to advocate on my behalf made a tremendous difference in my experience.\n\nIn an environment where quality customer service can sometimes be difficult to find, Jonathan consistently delivers a level of care, compassion, and professionalism that reflects the very best of Harlem Hospital. He treats every patient with dignity and respect and demonstrates the kind of commitment that organizations strive for but rarely find.\n\nHarlem Hospital is fortunate to have an employee like Jonathan Ortiz representing its mission and values. His dedication to helping patients access healthcare coverage is truly commendable, and I am grateful for all of his assistance.",
