          "description": "Over the years, my family and I have witnessed meaningful growth and positive change at Harlem Hospital. I truly appreciate the culture of compassion, dedication, and support demonstrated by the doctors\u2014like Dr. Weir, dentists such as Dr. Camper, and orthopedic specialists like Dr. Dayna Phillips as well as the entire staff. Their willingness to take the time to truly listen to their patients reflects a deep commitment to quality care and makes a lasting difference in the lives of those they serve. Their commitment not only impacts the quality of care but also inspires confidence and trust in the community. I\u2019m especially encouraged by the example this hospital sets for young aspiring Black children, like my daughters , who aspire to work in healthcare. It\u2019s powerful for them to see what\u2019s possible, and I look forward to the continued impact this institution will have on future generations in medicine.",
