          "description": "Referred to HHC/Harlem Dental at 15 w 136th Street, Extremely professional service by The DDS Dr.Rafid Inam and his Dental Assistant, They were extremely professional and very helpful and made my visit very smooth and tooth extraction were done very professionally without any discomfort. Walk in service is excellent, Building is cleaned and well maintained.\nHHC is always thriving and making it very easy for Patients and Employees to receive great medical services !",
