          "description": "I want to thank everyone at Harlem Hospital for all of their care and patience when I came in via ambulance straight to emergency room In a pretty dire and going through a terrible health scare. The doctor,nurses and staff were all very helpful and comforting when I was struggling with multiple issues. Dr. Sharp helped me so much with setting up much needed and long overdue healthcare information and aftercare. She even organized all necessary specialist and dental referral information and resources along with my discharge paperwork so that I can continue  getting my total health back on track again. I would recommend Harlem Hospital for any emergency health crisis and for all and any health care issues, specialists and providers.",
